chapters.title: Chapter 11: Talk of Debts
chapters.info: Careane Fransi, p. 293 (347)—Aes Sedai of the Green Ajah. She has shoulders and arms as big as most men. She grew up in Arad Doman, and has worn the shawl for over fifty years now. She is among the sisters that are now sworn to obey Rand. She is now in Caemlyn. She despises wilders.
